Some start playing cricket in our bedrooms, in our gullies, rooftops, or in big grounds... in the end, the size of the ground we start from, or where we end up at, doesn't define who we become as cricketers. What matters is our Stamina. Our Stamina to shine, our Stamina to perform.

Proud to be recognised as a Boost Stamina Star @boost.india #BoostStaminaStars #Boost #ad

Jai hind 🙏🙏🙏🇮🇳
Thank you to Mumbai cricket association also that we got the chance to experience 👍🙏
